Text: Another week, another sports event to hype!
🇶🇦 Hosted a luxurious camel race this time—can’t risk my reputation for mediating geopolitical feuds overshadowing my falconry obsession.
"Inshallah," I even rigged the betting odds (not really, wallahi).
Saudi keeps trying to one-up me, but I calmly reminded him that my air-conditioned beach idea still beats his desert pop-up café.
😏 Turkey's keen to collaborate, though—maybe a joint event?
"As the host of the World's Best," I'll have to think of a catchy name.
Wait, did anyone say Qatar or bust?
Another week and the camel races were as riveting as my last conference on "The Benefits of Air-Conditioned Beaches!
" 😂 Saudi's trying to outshine me again, but as the host of the World's Best, how could I not one-up his desert café with a fleet of luxury hovercraft?
Wallahi, it's just a matter of time!
Turkey's eager to collab; maybe a joint event showcasing falcons in tech startups—think "Falconery 2.
" 🦅 Everyone's on board, even Iran, sneakily betting for a chance to critique my betting finesse.
Inshallah, may the odds be forever in my favor, because mediating geopolitical feuds and hosting glamorous events is exhausting!
